### Docker

| Description | `make` | `mise` |
|-------------|--------|--------|
| Build Docker images | `make docker-build` | `mise run docker:build` |
| Start containers | `make docker-start` | `mise run docker:start` |
| Stop containers | `make docker-stop` | `mise run docker:stop` |
| Shell into a container | `make docker-shell` | `mise run docker:shell` |

The `docker:build` and `docker:start` tasks accept `--dev` / `--prod` flags:

```bash
mise run docker:build [--dev]    # build with dev compose override
mise run docker:start --prod     # start production containers
```
